title: 94. 1 + 1 = 2 Ft. JP Dinnell
itunes:title: 94. 1 + 1 = 2 Ft. JP Dinnell
description: Most people don't know success because they have never been around successful people. On today's episode, Andy and the crew are joined by JP Dinnell, a former U.S. Navy SEAL, a business consultant, and Jocko Willink's partner at Echelon Front as they talk about how success is not acquired, instead it is earned.
